# Workspace Reference — launchd-service

## Git SHA reference
```
repo: project-dashboard
origin: /Users/nateseluga/project-dashboard
sha: dd656f3
sha_full: dd656f3   # resolve with: git -C ~/project-dashboard rev-parse dd656f3
date: 2026-07-08T20:26:29-04:00
```

Rationale: the source session (7dd5bc6c) started 2026-07-09T00:46Z. dd656f3 is the
repo HEAD immediately before it — the exact state in which the task was posed.

## Tarball fallback
```
path: (to be generated) tasks/coding/launchd-service/workspace.tar.gz
build: git -C ~/project-dashboard archive --format=tar.gz -o <path> dd656f3
```

## Restore contract (proposed — see CONTRACT-NOTE.md)
The harness must materialize this state into a per-run temp dir, run `claude -p` with
that dir as cwd, and pass its path to check.sh as WORKSPACE_DIR. node_modules is NOT
in the tarball; the launchd check does not require an install (it only inspects the
plist/scripts as text), so no `npm install` is needed for this task.
